            • ACTION_MEASUREMENT_RESULT_CTH

              static final java.lang.String ACTION_MEASUREMENT_RESULT_CTH
              Callback indicating the result of health thermometer. The keyList of measurement result.
                KeyList:
                • CTH_INFO_UNIT_FLAG
                • CTH_RESULT
                • CTH_INFO_TS_FLAG
                • optional CTH_TS
                • CTH_INFO_TEMPERATURE_TYPE_FLAG
                • optional CTH_TEMPERATURE_TYPE
                eg. {"unit_flag":1,"result":96.30000305175781,"ts_flag":1,"ts":"2000-01-01 00:00:00","thermometer_type_flag":1,"thermometer_type":3}
